    <subfield code="y">00002 \footnotesize \it Integrated $\gamma$-ray emissivity (number of photons emitted per gas atom per unit time) constrained by Fermi-LAT (orange region \cite{Collaboration:2010cm}) compared with our predictions for $\tau=0,0.2,0.5,0.7,0.8,1.0$ (from top to bottom).</subfield>
  </datafield>
